<div id=title>
  Mushaf Layouts
</div>

<div id="body">
  <div class="modal-body">
    <% if false %>
      <p>
        Mushaf layout tool is used to create layout of any physal mushaf.
        Adjust pages, line alignment, and word placement on each line to accurately represent the Mushaf page.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-0">
        This page lists the available Mushaf layouts,
        including completed and in-progress designs.
        If you have a unique layout that you'd like to see added to QUL,
        feel free to submit a request
        on <%= link_to 'Github', 'https://github.com/TarteelAI/quranic-universal-library/issues/new/choose', target: '_blank', class: 'link-btn text-dark' %>
